Bank / Portugal sets 30 bln esc variable rate repo . The Bank of Portugal offered to inject 30 billion escudos of five - day funds into the money market in a variable rate securities repurchase tender . The central bank also offered to drain liquidity today with five - day certificates at a fixed rate of 5 . 80 percent . Its emergency lending rate for up to 100 billion escudos of one - day funds to resident banks stands at 7 . 80 percent . Bids for the repo funds must be submitted by 0900 GMT and bids for the certificates by 1400 GMT . - - Lisbon bureau 3511 - 3150035 
